1. *Pričaju* da se loše ponaša (They say he is behaving badly).
2. Oni *pričaju* ceo dan (They talk all day).
3. *Pričala* je o njegovom uspehu (She was talking about his success).
4. Oni *pričaju* o jutrošnjoj šetnji (They talk about the morning walk).
5. *Priča* se da će se to promeniti (It is said that this will change).
6. Ljudi *pričaju* da je njegova kuća u opasnosti (People are saying that his house is in danger).
7. Oni su *pričali* o školi (They were talking about school).
8. *Pričam* o tome kao o velikoj stvari (I am talking about it as a big thing).